{"type":"message","id":"7eb39c81","parentId":"09f56d39","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:53:50.663Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"668\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"667\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-02 15:53 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexaaa\",\n  \"body\": \"Oh no, that's a dangerous amount of pressure to put on me 😂\\n\\nAlright here's your Thursday starter pack:\\n\\n• 🍵 Make something warm to drink\\n• 🎵 Put on a playlist you haven't heard in a while\\n• 📱 Text that one friend you've been meaning to reach out to\\n\\nBoom. Thursday = interesting. You're welcome ✨\"\n}\n```\n\nOkay bro"}],"timestamp":1775145230661}}
