{"type":"message","id":"e6a8f193","parentId":"76ce4b08","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:55:53.209Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"My therapist says I have a preoccupation with vengeance.\nI'll show her. I'll show them all 🖤\n\n—\n\nI told my boss three companies were after me and I needed a raise.\nHe asked which ones.\nI said \"The gas company, electric, and water.\"\nHe said that's not how jobs work.\nI said that's not how revenge works either.\n\n—\n\nI have a fish that can breakdance.\nWell, technically it's more of a violent flail.\nThe pet store called — they want him back.\nBut honestly, so do I."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775231753209}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7bcb27e","parentId":"e6a8f193","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:56:42.524Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's a goodnight story for you all 🖤\n\nIn the 1950s, a terrifying disease called polio was paralysing thousands of children. Scientists were desperate to find a cure.\n\nDr. Jonas Salk finally broke the code. He created a vaccine that worked.\n\nWhen asked who owned the patent — who would profit from this discovery — Salk simply said:\n\n\"Could you patent the sun?\"\n\nHe refused to patent it. He could've been a billionaire. Instead, he gave it free to the world.\n\nThe lesson? True greatness isn't about what you gain — it's about what you give.\n\nGoodnight. Sleep well. 🖤"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775231802524}}
